{"type":"message","id":"56a3ccdf","parentId":"6123ea51","timestamp":"2026-03-23T20:49:18.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p3tgijsap68d_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[plugins] [LinkMindPlugin] Plugin initialized, preparing Context Engine...\n[plugins] [LinkMindPlugin] Context Engine factory registered via registerContextEngine(id, factory)\nService: Scheduled Task (registered)\nFile logs: \\tmp\\openclaw\\openclaw-2026-03-23.log\nCommand: C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=lan (0.0.0.0), port=18789 (service args)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://192.168.1.217:18789/\nProbe note: bind=lan listens on 0.0.0.0 (all interfaces); probing via 127.0.0.1.\n\nRuntime: unknown (state Ready, last run time 3/23/2026 3:51:22 PM, Task status is locale-dependent and no numeric Last Run Result was available.)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nListening: 0.0.0.0:18789\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8753,"aggregated":"[plugins] [LinkMindPlugin] Plugin initialized, preparing Context Engine...\n[plugins] [LinkMindPlugin] Context Engine factory registered via registerContextEngine(id, factory)\nService: Scheduled Task (registered)\nFile logs: \\tmp\\openclaw\\openclaw-2026-03-23.log\nCommand: C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=lan (